 last country home page theyÂ visited.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nWe are also not redirecting if the user isÂ editingÂ via the CMS, as this would stop them from editing theÂ globalÂ home page, as they would be redirected.<!--more-->','Using cookies to redirect a user to the last page they visted','','inherit','open','open','','18-revision-6','','','2010-02-27 00:06:19','2010-02-27 00:06:19','',18,'http://www.jonathansewell.co.uk/index.php/2010/02/27/18-revision-6/',0,'revision','',0);
